OL,7,FA police driver who crashed into a
OL,8,Fmother-of-three's car while chasing a
OL,9,Fsuspected stolen vehicle has appeared
OL,10,Fin court accused of causing her death
OL,11,Fby dangerous driving.
OL,13,FMark Burrows, 45, an officer with
OL,14,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP), was
OL,15,Fexcused from standing in the dock at
OL,16,FChester Crown Court as two charges
OL,17,Fwere put to him.
