OL,3,CPolice officer appears in court
OL,4,Caccused of causing death of woman from
OL,5,CStockport
OL,7,FBurrows, from Reddish, Stockport,
OL,8,Fpleaded not guilty to causing the
OL,9,Fdeath of Heather Smedley, 53, by
OL,10,Fdangerous driving and not guilty to a
OL,11,Fsecond charge of causing her death by
OL,12,Fcareless driving.
OL,14,FThe defendant, who spoke only to
OL,15,Fconfirm his name and enter his pleas,
OL,16,Fwas given unconditional bail until his
OL,17,Ftrial on April 27 2026.
