OL,7,FBurrows was at the wheel of an
OL,8,Funmarked police car pursuing an Audi
OL,9,FA3 that was suspected to have been
OL,10,Fstolen when the police car crashed
OL,11,Finto a Peugeot 108 driven by Ms
OL,12,FSmedley.
OL,14,FShe died at the scene of the crash,
OL,15,Faround 10am on December 23 2022 on
OL,16,FOldham Road and Otmoor Way in Oldham.
OL,18,FAfter her death, Ms Smedley's family
OL,19,Fpaid tribute to "the most kind,
OL,20,Fgentle, beautiful soul inside and out".
